How FreshBox Works

Freshbox is a subscription service that delivers your weekly fresh fruits and vegetables straight from local farmers.

Choose A Plan

First step, choose a plan suitable to your needs. This means how much produce you want to receive each week.

Set Your Preferences

Remember when mummy used to tell you eat all the veggies in your food? Well, with freshbox you can set your preferences and tell us what not to include in your box.

Enjoy Fresh Produce Everyday

Unsurprisingly, it is that simple. All you need to do is tell us what you want and for how many people, and freshbox will magically appear next to your door every week.
